619
01:05:37,798 --> 01:05:42,565
You now understand that the one neglected by the Levite and priest can be healed through Christ.

620
01:05:42,565 --> 01:05:46,786
You now understand that the prayers of the Church should not be denied to the humble.

621
01:05:46,786 --> 01:05:51,007
You now understand that the hands of priests should be extended to pitiable brothers.

622
01:05:51,007 --> 01:05:59,350
